OL,4,CWashington NFL team bans fans from
OL,5,Cwearing Native American dress
OL,6, The Washington Football Team, which
OL,7, dropped the controversial name Redskins
OL,8, last year, has now banned fans from
OL,9, wearing Native American headdresses and
OL,10, face paint at its home stadium.
OL,12,FThe new policy was among several the US
OL,13,FNFL team said would help provide the
OL,14,F"best possible fan experience for all".
OL,16,FThe Redskins name and logo was retired
OL,17,Fby the franchise in July last year.
OL,19,FIt followed years of pressure from
OL,20,Fgroups and sponsors who criticised the
OL,21,Fname as offensive to Native Americans.
